
@submissionId = REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID
@problemId = REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID

### Submit Code (Requires Auth Cookie)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/submissions
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "problemId": "{{problemId}}",
    "code": "print('hello world')",
    "language": "python"
}

### Get All Submissions (Requires Auth Cookie)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/submissions

### Get Submissions for Problem (Requires Auth Cookie)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/submissions/problem/{{problemId}}

### Get Single Submission (Requires Auth Cookie)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/submissions/{{submissionId}}
